                h3  Contribution 
                p As project lead, I led our team in determining the area of intervention and framing. As content strategist I determined the content design of the site (the lesson plan in particular) and wrote its corresponding copy. As UX/UI designer, I conducted user interviews/research, and co-designed the site's user flow and user interface.


                h3  Brief 
