            section.grid.x12c 


                h2  Insights  
                p Synthesizing the research gave me 4 key insights to drive our intervention

                ul.big

                    +faList("Second language teachers use cultural heritage to bring personal bearing to language education.")(class="fas fa-lightbulb-on")
                    +faList("Educators, need age-specific, modular actionable lesson resources.")(class="fas fa-lightbulb-on")
                    +faList("Open-ended middle school curriculum = freedom to bring in external topics such as World Heritage.")(class="fas fa-lightbulb-on")
                    +faList("World Heritage is eurocentric and so finding resources on lesser-known non-european Heritage Sites is difficult.")(class="fas fa-lightbulb-on")

